                    <div class="row g-0">
                        <div class="col-md-4 lead-card-img-holder overflow-hidden">
                            <img src="images/projects/project-4.jpg" class="card-img rounded-0" alt="...">
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-8 d-flex flex-column align-content-between">
                            <div class="card-body ">
                                <h5 class="card-title fw-bolder border-bottom border-2 d-inline border-primary">Bug Tracker</h5>
                                <p class="card-text mt-3">The Bug Tracker is a project that resolves specific bussiness need- the ability to report, manage and resolve bugs in the company. It is an .NET MVC project that uses Bootstrap5, Postgresql database and Entity Framework.</p>

                            </div>
                            <div class="card-footer">
                                <small class="text-muted">Last updated 3 mins ago</small>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="link-mask">
                        <div class="link-mask-link">
                            <a class="btn btn-dark" href="#"> <i class="fas fa-eye me-3"></i>View Details</a>
                        </div>
